

Areas of further work
=====================

1) CICD - wire the Terraform code into the GitHub Actions Workflow
2) EFS - mount the EFS mount targets and move the static content to the EFS
3) Create a fancy name (nickname) for your Application Load Balancer (ALB) and using Route 53 create an entry for your ALB
4) Security of secrets - design and implement a way of securing the DB secrets and remove them from the code.
5) Design a plan for usinf SSL/TLS on the ALB
6) Observability - Design an observability strategy for the system
7) Design a plan for upgrading the deployment
